{"title":"乡村小学","authors":["李汉荣"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":5,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡村小学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李汉荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云从窗口飘进来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被孩子们裁成试卷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"填写对生活的猜想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝴蝶和蜜蜂常来偷听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们不交学费"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只带来一些山野的清香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上的燕子总爱抢着发言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满嘴的南方口音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连我们的老师也听不懂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瀑布和松涛也争着给我们讲课"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但它们连小学也没有毕业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪有我们的女老师讲得动听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天，我们在她的故事里取暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天，我们在她的歌声里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘凉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷说：她就是我们山里的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚，我看见山腰上亮着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一盏小灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是不是她的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着我们的梦境"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}